.rule_4_5_2_ensure_rip_is_set_to_check_for_zero_values_in_reserved_fields

Reference: Configuration Guide, Juniper Networks

Remediation: If you have deployed RIP in your network and disabled zero value checking of reserved
fields, you should re-enable it by issuing the following command from the [edit protocols
rip] hierarchy:
[edit protocols rip]
user@host#set check-zero





